headline: IDEXX Laboratories to Release 2025 Third Quarter Financial Results
summary: WESTBROOK, Maine, October 08, 2025--IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (NASDAQ: IDXX), a global leader in pet healthcare innovation, has scheduled the release of its 2025 third quarter financial results for Monday, November 3, 2025, before the market opens. The Company will conduct an analyst conference call beginning at 8:30 a.m. ET on that day.
